<div class="pl6-ns pr6-ns pt5-ns pl3 pr3 pt4">
  <h1 class="fw4-ns f1-ns f2 fw5 orange">
    Get Involved
  </h1>

  <p class="f2-l fw3-l f4 ">
    <span class="courier">:bgt</span> wouldn't be what it is now without the help of our supporters and those around who have offered their time, money and services to help us grow. If you would like to get involved and support us, find out how below.
  </p>

  <div class="f2-l fl-l w-100-l f4 tc">
    <div class="w-third-l fl-l pa2-l">
      <i class="fa fa-heart-o" aria-hidden="true" style="font-size:5vw; color:white;"></i>
      <h2 class="pink-local grow dim">
        <%= link_to "Volunteer", volunteer_path %>
      </h2>
    </div>

    <div class="w-third-l fl-l pa2-l">
      <i class="fa fa-pencil" aria-hidden="true" style="font-size:5vw;color:white;"></i>
      <h2 class="pink-local grow dim">
        <%= link_to "Contribute", contribute_path %>
      </h2>
    </div>

    <div class="w-third-l fl-l pa2-l">
      <i class="fa fa-money" aria-hidden="true" style="font-size:5vw; color:white;"></i>
      <h2 class="pink-local grow dim">
        <%= link_to "Donate", donate_path %>
      </h2>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
